@startuml
!theme vibrant
title Comment on Post Sequence

actor User

box "Favi-BE Backend" #LightBlue
  participant "CommentsController" as CommentController
  participant "ICommentService" as CommentService
end box

User -> CommentController: POST /api/comments\n(CreateCommentRequest)
activate CommentController

CommentController -> CommentService: CreateAsync(postId, userId, content, parentId)
activate CommentService
CommentService --> CommentController: CommentResponse
deactivate CommentService

CommentController --> User: 200 OK (CommentResponse)
deactivate CommentController
@enduml
